---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="section-label">Sobre mi</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Lo que me mueve</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="about-card-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"/>
            <path d="M2 12h20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Futbol</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Tanto jugarlo como verlo. El futbol me ensena trabajo en equipo,
          estrategia y la importancia de mantener la disciplina.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="about-card-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/>
            <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/>
            <line x1="14" y1="4" x2="10" y2="20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Backend Development</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Me apasiona disenar arquitecturas robustas, APIs escalables
          y sistemas que funcionen con solidez bajo presion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-card glass-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="about-card-icon">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/>
            <line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="about-card-title">Retos del Frontend</h3>
        <p class="about-card-text">
          Disfruto transformar disenos en interfaces pixel-perfect,
          resolviendo los puzzles que cada UI presenta.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-card-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--accent-glow);
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: background var(--transition-base),
                transform var(--transition-base);
  }

  .about-card:hover .about-card-icon {
    background: var(--accent-glow-strong);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .about-card-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-card-text {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
